{"title":"沂蒙顶针","authors":["厉彦林"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":9,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沂蒙顶针"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厉彦林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜顶针"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待嫁的闺女，过门的媳妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一不比戒指，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二不赛耳环，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴枚黄铜顶针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既实用又耐看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田埂地堰，树下碾边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扔下锄头喘口气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针线笸箩就坐一圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你缝抗夏的单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我连御寒的棉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心比针眼儿细，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼比针尖儿尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮爬上西山口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一针刺痛黎明的哈欠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这手工针线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴身、暖和、耐穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表达实打实的情感。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使针线歪歪扭扭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也舒心顺眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怪不得闺女出嫁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先为自己绣一对鸳鸯枕头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一幅喜鹊登枝的窗帘。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}